The goal is `r := ...` where `r` is the reflexivity part of the `Setoid` structure.
`r` is `∃ (s : Equiv.Perm (Fin n)), ∃ (h_eq : s p.1 = q.1), h_eq ▸ (permMapWalk n s p.2) = q.2`.
We use `s = Equiv.refl` and `h_eq = rfl`.
